text: Ishteryakovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Karabashevsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 492 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Verkhneyarkeyevo, 2 km from Karabashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District
title: Ishteryakovo
